title: For Sale:  CA-LEGAL DPMS AR-15 223/556 1:9 16" WITH UPGRADES AND BAG
postcontent: For sale is a DPMS AR-15 223/556 16" 1:9 twist barrel with several upgrades and rifle bag.Cosmetic: 9/10 (some very minor wears that are hardly noticeable). Functionality: 10/10 (it has been performing flawlessly even with bulk reload ammo).The barrel is 16" length, 1:9 twist, and chambered in 556 so it will shoot both 223 and 556. The rifle was purchased brand new from Turner's Outdoor couple years ago and has had roughly 1000 rounds through the barrel. Upgrades include:- JP enterprise 3.5 lbs trigger spring kit which significantly reduces the trigger pull, but is still strong enough to fire all the bulk ammo we have been using.- Trigger job (polishing) so the pull is crisp with clean break.- Magpul rubber grip- Magpul foregrip- Hexmag (10-rd) magazine- Rubber stock pad- NcSTAR quadrail- Extended takedown pins (front and rear)- BAD-style magazine lock pinAlso comes with black M4 rifle bag.It is fully CA legal after the bullet button ban. The rifle is fitted with magazine lock pin similar to that of Battle Arms Development (BAD). When the action is closed, the pin is depressed and prevents the magazine release button from working, thus the magazine is fixed. When the action is open, the pin is pushed up by a spring, allowing the magazine release button to work and release the magazine. The spring is not too strong so it will not push the pin all the way out. The pin also won't come out even when you turn the rifle up-side-down with shaking. So you don't have to worry about losing the pin for whatever reason. To remove the pin, you will need a small plier or tweezer to pull it out. Both takedown pins are upgraded to extended length which allows quick takedown of the action to release the magazine.Price: $400Meet at Turner Outdoor in Torrance for PPTAddress: 18305 Hawthorne Blvd, Torrance, CA 90504PPT only, buyer pays transfer fee, no shipping, no trade, no cash-and-carry or off-the-record.If ads is still up, the gun is still available.
